  • Description: SequenceEvent: The leaking hazmat was discovered in the unload upon opening the trailer that contained this shipment. DescribePack: One of the four total bottles had a loose cap. Coincidentally, that is the bottle that leaked contents. DurationRel: 1 and MitigateEffect: Swift action taken by an operations administrator mitigated the release time. The spill was promptly called out on the radio which surely helped. The shipment was contained in a hazardous material bag and hazardous materials spill tote shortly thereafter.
